                                                  kufāle</title>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">ዝንቱ፡ ነገረ፡ ኩፋሌ፡ መዋዕል፡ ለሕግ፡ ወለስምዕ፡ ለግብረ፡ ዓመታት፡
                  በተሰብዖቶሙ፡ ለኢየቤላስቲሆሙ፡ ውስተ፡ ኵሉ፡ ዓመታተ፡ ዓለም፡ በከመ፡ ተናገሮ፡ እግዚእ፡ ለሙሴ፡ በደብረ፡ ሲና፡ አመ፡ ዐርገ፡ ይንሣእ፡
                  ፪፡ ጽላተ፡ ዘሕግ፡ ወዘትእዛዝ፡ በቃለ፡ እግዚኣብሔር፡ በከመ፡ ይቤሎ፡ ዕረግ፡ ውስተ፡ ርእሰ፡ ደብር።</incipit>
                     <note>This manuscript represents an older version than those used for the edition  
                  <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/RM3CUPK4"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Dillmann1859Kufale"/><title level="m">መጽሐፈ፡ ኩፋሌ፡ (Maṣḥafa kufāle) sive Liber Jubilaeorum qui idem a Graecis &lt;hi rend="italics"&gt;η λεπτη γενεσις&lt;/hi&gt; inscribitur : versione Graeca deperdita nunc nonnisi in Geez lingua conservatus nuper ex Abyssini in Europam allatus</title><author><forename>August</forename><surname>Dillmann</surname></author><pubPlace>Kiliae–Londini</pubPlace><publisher>apud C. G. I. van Maack–apud Williams et Norgate</publisher><date>1859</date><note type="url">https://archive.org/details/liberjubilaeorum00dilluoft</note><note type="tags"><note type="tag">bm:Dillmann1859Kufale</note><note type="tag">Jubilees</note></note><note type="tag">bm:Dillmann1859Kufale</note><note type="tag">Jubilees</note></bibl> 
                  and translation <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/2WJZG9ZU"><seg type="bookSection"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Dillmann1850Jubilaeen"/><title level="a">Das Buch der Jubiläen oder die kleine Genesis</title><title level="m">Jahrbücher der biblischen Wissenschaft</title><author><forename>August</forename><surname>Dillmann</surname></author><pubPlace>Göttingen</pubPlace><publisher>In der Dieterichschen Buchhandlung</publisher><date>1850</date><biblScope unit="volume">II: 1849</biblScope><biblScope unit="page">230-256</biblScope><note type="url">https://books.google.de/books?id=S34bAQAAIAAJ&amp;printsec=frontcover&amp;hl=fr&amp;source=gbs_ge_summary_r&amp;cad=0#v=onepage&amp;q&amp;f=false</note><note type="tags"><note type="tag">Jubilees</note><note type="tag">bm:Dillmann1850Jubilaeen</note></note><note type="tag">Jubilees</note><note type="tag">bm:Dillmann1850Jubilaeen</note></bibl>.
                For a list of the most noteworthy variants for the first twenty pages of the printed edition, see <ref target="#"/>.</note> 
                     
